*mpv-0.1.7 (22 Sep 2013)

  22 Sep 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@gmx.us> -mpv-0.1.4.ebuild, +mpv-0.1.7.ebuild,
  mpv-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  version bump, add USE doc-pdf, macosx options were removed from configure,
  fix libva dep

*mpv-0.1.4 (31 Aug 2013)

  31 Aug 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> -mpv-0_p20130615.ebuild,
  -mpv-0_p20130715.ebuild, +mpv-0.1.4.ebuild, mpv-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  add upstream release, USE vaapi, update ffmpeg dep

*mpv-0_p20130715 (15 Jul 2013)

  15 Jul 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> +mpv-0_p20130715.ebuild:
  new snapshot

  11 Jul 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mpv-9999.ebuild:
  keep build reproducible

  09 Jul 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mpv-9999.ebuild:
  do not add -g to CFLAGS

  09 Jul 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mpv-9999.ebuild:
  fix USE threads, install more DOCS, rm obsolete USE fbcon

  08 Jul 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mpv-9999.ebuild:
  upstream removed several configure options, fix USE deps, add USE threads,
  hide upstream CFLAGS warning, radio builds fine without oss, remove USE debug
  (it only changes CFLAGS now), build fails with ffmpeg-1, cosmetics

  05 Jul 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mpv-9999.ebuild:
  fix USE quvi

  04 Jul 2013; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mpv-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  upstream added libguess support

